snippet.title: Best VGM 1404 - Dragon Ball Z Butouden 3 - Tenkaichi Budoukai
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Dragon Ball Z Butouden 3 (1994)
Tenkaichi Budoukai
Shinji Amagishi, Chatrasch, Switch. E & Kenji Yamamoto
